    {"type": "bulleted_list_item", "bulleted_list_item": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "能力圈原则：清楚界定自己真正理解的领域，在边界内操作"}}]}},
    {"type": "bulleted_list_item", "bulleted_list_item": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "逆向思维：\"反过来想，总是反过来想\" — 先想如何失败，再避免它"}}]}},
    {"type": "bulleted_list_item", "bulleted_list_item": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "考虑二阶、三阶后果：不满足于表面答案，思考连锁反应"}}]}},
    {"type": "bulleted_list_item", "bulleted_list_item": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "安全边际：为错误留出足够空间"}}]}},

    {"type": "heading_3", "heading_3": {"rich_text": [{"type": "text", "text": {"content": "普世智慧"}}]}},
